202
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:25,000
So you got yourself, it was called a dance card, and you went around to your friends, and the fraternity, you exchanged dances. You came with your girlfriend of course, but you exchanged dances, you didn't dance with her the whole evening.

203
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:35,000
So you generally saved the last dance, and the first dancer yourself, and a couple in between, and then you would be trading off with friends.

204
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:45,000
