207
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:28,000
If I remember this correctly, closing hours in all women's groups, there were very few married students, very few on the campus.

208
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:34,000
I only knew one, one couple, in chemistry.

209
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:42,000
